1.title: Meet the Parents

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

1.plot: Four singles - Maravic, Mitch, Christina and John - who have been unlucky in love decide to let their parents pick the person they should marry. Their parents will "date" their prospective suitors first in hopes of finding "the one."

2.title: Date My Parents

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

2.plot: Mitch's parents go on a final date and prep him to meet their final choices. Christina's parents propose to the man they want her to marry. Marivic's best friend is shocked to hear that she's letting her parents pick her spouse. And we meet John.

3.title: Cut the Bull$#!%

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

3.plot: Mitch goes on dates with two potential wives his parents picked. John's parents meet his first possible match while he reveals to his friends he's getting married. Marivic's parents go on their last date. And Christina reluctantly meets her parent's pick

4.title: Cold Feet

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

4.plot: Christina and her family face a major hurdle on her wedding day. Mitch goes on his last date before his parents pick his wife. And John's parents meet Kristina and prepare to pick his wife.

5.title: Red Flags

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

5.plot: Mitch's parents pick his bride and Mitch proposes to her. John goes on dates with his potential brides. Christina and her parents decide what they should do next. Marivic goes on a date and clashes with her father.

6.title: I'm Done

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

6.plot: Marivic and her dad argue about her suitors. Mitch's fiancée, buys a wedding dress but is still keeping the wedding a secret from her family. John's parents propose to their top pick. Christina's parents continue their search for her husband.

7.title: The Big Reveal

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

7.plot: Mitch and Emily get married. John's parents propose to their top suitor on his behalf. Marivic talks to Edna to see if she'll continue on despite Manny quitting. Derald and Becky think they have finally found Christina's perfect match.

8.title: It's Over

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

8.plot: John's parents introduce him to his future wife. During Mitch and Emily's honeymoon, Emily's trust issues become apparent. Christina is anxious to meet her future husband at the altar. Manny decides to make amends with Marivic.

9.title: Second Thoughts

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

9.plot: Christina and Tom contend with sleeping arrangement on their first night together as a married couple. Mitch and Emily's honeymoon ends on a rocky note. John is anxious about his upcoming wedding to Chandler.

10.title: Happily Ever After?

episode of.title: Married by Mom and Dad (TV Series 2015– )

10.plot: Mitch & Emily's differences come to a head, after his sexuality is questioned by Emily's friend. Christina is unsure whether she can live with Tom. And John has to decide if he can take those final steps to the altar.
